@startuml NetPulse_类图_四层分层_与实体图配套
' =============================================================================
' 与「领域实体类图」配套：实体图侧重对象与关联；本图侧重 Spring 典型四层依赖。
' 题注建议：图4-x NetPulse 后端分层类图（Controller / Service / Repository / Entity）
' =============================================================================
!theme plain
skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam linetype polyline
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam roundcorner 8
skinparam nodesep 28
skinparam ranksep 32
hide empty methods
top to bottom direction
scale max 1800 width

title NetPulse 后端四层类图（与领域实体图配套）

note as N
  **说明**：领域实体类图突出 **数据对象、多重性与业务关联**；
  本图突出 **控制层 → 服务层 → 持久层 → 实体** 的调用与依赖方向。
  少数 CRUD 控制器可直接注入仓储（如告警规则管理），图中一并标出，避免与「必须经过 Service」的教条冲突。
end note

package "① 控制层 Controller" #dae8fc {
  class AuthController
  class DeviceController
  class AlertController
  class AlarmRulesController
  class AiChatController
}

package "② 业务层 Service" #d5e8d4 {
  class UserService
  class DeviceService
  class AlertService
  class AiChatService
  class AuditService
}

package "③ 持久层 Repository" #fff2cc {
  interface SysUserRepository <<interface>>
  interface DeviceRepository <<interface>>
  interface AlertRuleRepository <<interface>>
  interface AlarmRulesRepository <<interface>>
  interface AiChatSessionRepository <<interface>>
}

package "④ 领域实体 Entity" #e1d5e7 {
  class SysUser
  class Device
  class AlertRule
  class AlarmRules
  class AiChatSession
}

' ---------- Controller → Service ----------
AuthController --> UserService : 登录校验
AuthController --> AuditService : 登录审计
DeviceController --> DeviceService : 业务编排
DeviceController --> AuditService : 操作审计
AlertController --> AlertService : 规则/历史
AlertController --> AuditService : 操作审计
AiChatController --> AiChatService : 对话与上下文
AiChatController --> AuditService : 操作审计

' ---------- 直接 Controller → Repository（薄 CRUD）----------
AlarmRulesController --> AlarmRulesRepository : CRUD
AlarmRulesController --> AuditService : 规则审计

' ---------- Service → Repository ----------
UserService --> SysUserRepository
DeviceService --> DeviceRepository
AlertService --> AlertRuleRepository
AiChatService --> AiChatSessionRepository
note right of AuditService
  审计写入经 **AuditLogRepository**
  落库至 AuditLog（图中从略）
end note

' ---------- Repository → Entity ----------
SysUserRepository ..> SysUser : JPA ORM
DeviceRepository ..> Device
AlertRuleRepository ..> AlertRule
AlarmRulesRepository ..> AlarmRules
AiChatSessionRepository ..> AiChatSession

legend right
  |= 与多张类图的分工 |
  | **领域实体图**：表结构视角的类与关系 |
  | **本图**：分层架构视角的依赖方向 |
  | **全量分层**：见 `NetPulse-类图-论文新版-分层.puml` |
endlegend

@enduml
